Artistic Wat Rong Khun, Chiang Rai Thailand - Wat Rong Khun or White Temple is a contemporary n unconventional buddhist temple in northern thailand. Considered as one of the most beautiful temple on earth it's got a name from exterior white structure covered with fragments of mirrored glass. Inside the temple, the decor swiftly moves from pristine white to fiery n bewildering.
